com.fatwire.gst.foundation.facade.assetapi.asset

Class AssetMapAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<String,Object>
      • com.fatwire.gst.foundation.facade.assetapi.asset.AssetMapAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,Object>

    public class AssetMapAdapter
extends AbstractMap<String,Object>
implements Map<String,Object>
    This class adapts an TemplateAsset into a Map. The Map is convenient in expression languages like JSP EL.

    This class uses lazy-loading, so if used in a View layer, it might open connections to the database.

    In case of naming conflicts with flex attribute names and meta attribute names the meta attributes take precedent.

    Since:
    Nov 23,2009
